description:
This is a 20 minute workout called '20 Minute Chakra Balance & Cleansing Guided Meditation' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This meditation guides you through each chakra point to release stagnant energy and restore balance.  By dedicating a mere 20 minutes to this practice, you invest in your holistic well-being, promoting physical, emotional, and spiritual equilibrium.  Allow the soothing guidance to cleanse and align your chakras, rejuvenating your energy centers and leaving you with a profound sense of clarity.  Embrace this opportunity to reconnect with your inner self, revitalizing your spirit and promoting a harmonious balance in your daily life.  This is an Original 20 minute guided  meditation recorded by us.  

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!  
We appreciate all your support and contribution to allow this channel to continue to share our guided meditations with the world.  Thank you!!!
